                      <font face="Arial" size="1" color="#555555"><i>Click to view full screenshot</i></font>
                    </figcaption>
                  </figure>
                </td>

                <td>
                  <font face="Arial" size="2">
                    <p><b>Description:</b><br />
                    An HTML information page on cyber security topics including
                    phishing, ransomware, and the
                    <abbr title="Confidentiality, Integrity, Availability">CIA</abbr> Triad.
                    Demonstrates the use of tables, figures, blockquotes,
                    <code>meter</code>, <code>progress</code>, and semantic HTML5 tags.</p>

                    <p><b>Tools used:</b> Notepad, HTML5</p>

                    <p><b>Year:</b> <time datetime="2026">2026</time></p>

                    <p>
                      <b>Reference:</b>
                      <a href="https://www.cisa.gov/" target="_blank">CISA Official Website &#8599;</a>
                    </p>
                  </font>
                </td>

              </tr>
